{"tid":444263,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩開始去健身室做GYM,求指教","createTime":"2017-10-22T11:03:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-23T14:31:30.000Z","uid":15501,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"69f5107c65dc4f24767375e06e5e52d238b81202","tid":444263,"uid":15501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T11:03:09.000Z","msg":"今日第一次正式去健身做GYM<br />\n想問下巴打點樣安排每星期做幾多日,每次去做D咩<br />\n<br />\n本身一星期會有3日倣下掌上壓SITUP 深蹲,40-50下,做三組,跟住一日練泰拳<br />\n有FD話我有少少線條,但我想再大隻多少少<br />\n<br />\n應該每個星期點練<br />\n<br />\n利申今日正係去做機飛鳥6組練胸,6組機練背同4組練下三頭肌"},{"pid":"ea9eaae28d13cd3869f4da1bc18f9290bd8a6b93","tid":444263,"uid":15501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T11:07:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb6ec76fd0ee6a37ae3b0239a4f3dd1fa023e106","tid":444263,"uid":13802,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T11:08:05.000Z","msg":"一組40-50下 你應該係好有線條喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c59a220558a32420a224c3752584fe98319b9ca","tid":444263,"uid":90634,"like":1,"dislike":20,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T11:18:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一組40-50下 你應該係好有線條喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁講就知你未做過gym<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa518af1f0a25211a65dec604061912972da8490","tid":444263,"uid":15501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T11:22:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b30e57915a940efe683fc8fd94b31744691796","tid":444263,"uid":15501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T12:44:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebcbc96d7c3c7d7d8799ce1df2e06ab8c9d8c814","tid":444263,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime