ssets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁應該點 求指點"},{"pid":"7cebe36a2546ed28d3eab9c1da79524c21e1fb28","tid":444263,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T14:03:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.gymbeginner.hk/2015/11/16/%E5%81%A5%E8%BA%AB%E6%96%B0%E6%89%8B28%E5%A4%A9%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gymbeginner.hk%2F2015%2F11%2F16%2F%25E5%2581%25A5%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%2589%258B28%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E8%25A8%2593%25E7%25B7%25B4%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583%2F&d=uNgeisI3UP3VmGMXQXy0TxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=09c2e874\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.gymbeginner.hk/2015/11/16/%E5%81%A5%E8%BA%AB%E6%96%B0%E6%89%8B28%E5%A4%A9%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83/</a><br />\n利申:Google搵 唔想慢慢打字<br />\n新手基本都係咁上下 <br />\n主要動作玩得好唔好 有無feel咁上下"},{"pid":"49ed27d5059d065eef660b9d1b41fbff7931faed","tid":444263,"uid":15501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T14:06:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.gymbeginner.hk/2015/11/16/%E5%81%A5%E8%BA%AB%E6%96%B0%E6%89%8B28%E5%A4%A9%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gymbeginner.hk%2F2015%2F11%2F16%2F%25E5%2581%25A5%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%2589%258B28%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E8%25A8%2593%25E7%25B7%25B4%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583%2F&d=uNgeisI3UP3VmGMXQXy0TxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=09c2e874\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.gymbeginner.hk/2015/11/16/%E5%81%A5%E8%BA%AB%E6%96%B0%E6%89%8B28%E5%A4%A9%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83/</a><br />\n利申:Google搵 唔想慢慢打字<br />\n新手基本都係咁上下 <br />\n主要動作玩得好唔好 有無feel咁上下</blockquote><br />\n咁我平時做開掌上壓係唔係可以唔做<br />\n<br />\n我練開掌會唔會體能下解埋"},{"pid":"b835697165d9140c72f46f4f03e26442bfe2bdc9","tid":444263,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T14:12:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://www.gymbeginner.hk/2015/11/16/%E5%81%A5%E8%BA%AB%E6%96%B0%E6%89%8B28%E5%A4%A9%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gymbeginner.hk%2F2015%2F11%2F16%2F%25E5%2581%25A5%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%2589%258B28%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E8%25A8%2593%25E7%25B7%25B4%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583%2F&d=uNgeisI3UP3VmGMXQXy0TxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=09c2e874\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.gymbeginner.hk/2015/11/16/%E5%81%A5%E8%BA%AB%E6%96%B0%E6%89%8B28%E5%A4%A9%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83/</a><br />\n利申:Google搵 唔想慢慢打字<br />\n新手基本都係咁上下 <br />\n主要動作玩得好唔好 有無feel咁上下</blockquote><br />\n咁我平時做開掌上壓係唔係可以唔做<br />\n<br />\n我練開掌會唔會體能下解埋</blockquote><br />\n拳上壓我個人建議你操胸果一日放係最後做<br />\n大約20-25下一隻 約做2組左右你應該收皮<br />\n如果仲有力代表你hea操/你要玩進階d<br />\n最後果句唔明咩 咩操開拳 解埋?"},{"pid":"15c7c34ffe6dbdb39e99d4b00727505380de651c","tid":444263,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T14:12:27.000Z","msg":"我都打錯左 掌上壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3c9330bba3c5495a89816177f04f52d86f67143","tid":444263,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T14:14:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d37698ebd3b132377514caafc292a536d4b5c67d","tid":444263,"uid":58140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T14:17:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又胸又背又三頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n計動作你又太少 組數太多 <br />\n唔好乜都玩 應主力一個大組肌肉 有力可配一個小肌肉一齊練</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有小小唔明點樣淨係主力一組肌肉，唔係正常應該做幾set就收皮架咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真心求教</blockquote><br />\n咁你果日玩胸咪玩胸 玩背咪玩背<br />\n點樣2種大肌肉一齊玩<br />\n同埋你點樣做幾set就無力 唔識用力 唔知自己大約玩幾重?<br />\n引用<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.joiiup.com/knowledge/content/768\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=ht